---
title: Warm Apple, Feta & Mixed Greens Salad with Walnut Panko & Blue Cheese Dressing
description: This festive main course salad is destined to become a hit on your table! You’ll toss a bright mix of fresh greens, tender sautéed apple, and quick-pickled shallot with creamy blue cheese dressing and briny crumbled feta. Shower your salad with crunchy walnut-panko topping for a harmonious blend of flavors and textures.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/670e78cd39e665b06a0c87fc-ea1117f7.jpeg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/670e78cd39e665b06a0c87fc-en-US.pdf
course: main course
servings: 2
cuisine: North America
time required: 20 minutes
nutrition:
  calories: 440 kcal
  fat: 30 g
  saturated fat: 12 g
  carbohydrates: 33 g
  sugar: 16 g
  protein: 8 g
  fiber: 5 g
  sodium: 930 mg
author: HelloFresh
